âœ… Scalability:

Spam filters (e.g., Gmail) block 99.9% of phishing by hard rules (Google 2023 Security Report).

When Harmful
âŒ Brittleness:

Tay by Microsoft (2016): Hackers exploited its lack of moral reasoning to teach it racism within 24 hours.

